Exp 10.12: RadioButton and RadioButton Group
Aim
To design an application using RadioButton and RadioGroup to select one option from multiple choices.

Algorithm
1.Start
2.Create a layout with a RadioGroup
3.Add multiple RadioButtons inside the RadioGroup
4.Assign unique IDs to each RadioButton
5.Wait for the user to select one option
6.On button click (or event):
 Check which RadioButton is selected using RadioGroup
7.Display the selected option (using TextView/Toast)
8.Stop
